data.expected_result: I would expect the text say "Mutual Servers". It's a visualizer after all
data.short_description: In the Rich Presence Visualizer, the 2nd tab in the Full Profile example says "Mutual Guilds" instead of "Mutual Servers"
data.steps_to_repro: - Go to the dev portal - Create, or use an existing application - Select the Rich Presence tab on the left - Scroll down to the Visualizer - Observe how the text is inconsistent with what's actually in the profile
